          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1758505229" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11039962297972448711">A mixture of the genuine historical figures, Pakistan&apos;s General Zia through to the fictitious narrator Ali Shigri the author has managed to produce a satire that, along with some genuine laugh out loud comic moments, made this a very good read that should stand the test of time. </span>
  <span id="freeText11039962297972448711" style="display:none">A mixture of the genuine historical figures, Pakistan's General Zia through to the fictitious narrator Ali Shigri the author has managed to produce a satire that, along with some genuine laugh out loud comic moments, made this a very good read that should stand the test of time. </span>
  <a data-text-id="11039962297972448711" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

